# OneDrive Configuration
# Get your Client ID from: https://portal.azure.com → Azure Active Directory → App registrations
# Replace 'your-client-id-here' with your actual Azure AD Client ID
ONEDRIVE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id-here

# Optional: OneDrive Application Secret (for server-side apps only)
# ONEDRIVE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret-here

# Optional: Custom redirect URI (defaults to Microsoft's native client URI)
# ONEDRIVE_REDIRECT_URI=https://login.microsoftonline.com/common/oauth2/nativeclient

# Optional: Custom scopes (defaults to files.readwrite offline_access)
# ONEDRIVE_SCOPES=files.readwrite offline_access

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env in the project root
# 2. Replace the dummy values with your actual Azure AD app credentials
# 3. Register your app at: https://portal.azure.com → Azure Active Directory → App registrations
# 4. Never commit the .env file to version control 